{
  "arquivo": "op_03_01",
  "total": 77,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(The after-party has ended.\\n It's about time. They should be coming soon.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(...They will come, won't they?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(On the second night of the school festival,\\n on the way back, Ichika asked me to buy drinks at the park...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Nino wants black tea, Miku wants green tea,\\nYotsuba wants juice, and Itsuki-chan wants coffee.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Who would I choose?\\n I answered the question\\n by not buying anything.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(On the first day of the school festival,\\n I had already decided not to choose anyone,\\n to show that my feelings wouldn't change.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Ichika was clearly disappointed. No, maybe she was\\n beyond exasperated that I'm the worst,\\n a useless idiot who always depends on others.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(From the way she acted, Ichika may not come after all.\\n If she talked to the other four,\\n they may not come either.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(But, it's not like I haven't thought about it.\\n I believe this is the best way,\\n so I called all of you here.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "!!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Excuse me!\\nIs Uesugi-san here?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, I am.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "What are you doing in this dark place?\\nCan you turn on the lights?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Ah, well, it's not like I'm in the mood for that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Oh, I see.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "It's bright outside, so it's enough, I guess.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Yeah.\\nThe night festival technically ended,\\nbut everyone's still making noise.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Just because there was an announcement,\\nit doesn't mean it's over, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "So, Fu-kun?\\nThe final day is already over, but%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "You called us out here for that reason, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yeah.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Then, let us hear it.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Okay.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I won't choose anyone.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "...Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Wha...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "*sigh*",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Wait a minute.\\nUm, well, what exactly does that mean?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Exactly that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Are you serious?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Of course.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Don't fool around.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Nino...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Even if it's you, Fu-kun, there are things\\nthat can be forgiven and things that can't. I can't\\nbelieve you won't make a choice at this point...!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I won't accept this either.\\nThis is not an answer.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No, it's a legit answer.\\nIt's just not what you wanted.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "You...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Futaro-kun.\\nI don't think you should talk like that.\\nYou're hurting yourself too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Uesugi-kun, I'll speak my mind here without hesitation.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "This is the same as not giving an answer.\\nI feel like you're just running away.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "I also can't accept this!\\nUesugi-san, this is too much!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Don't just stay silent, say something!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(I knew it wouldn't be easy to accept.\\n I knew that, but...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Fu-kun!!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Futaro...!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Uesugi-san...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Hey, is this really okay?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Shit...!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "...I understand.\\nBut no matter what anyone says,\\nmy feelings won't change.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "I'll keep doing what I've been doing.\\nI'll make you face me in my own way, Fu-kun!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Me too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Sorry, but my feelings also aren't going to change.\\nYou should stop. It's a waste of time.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Uesugi-kun!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 63,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Did I say too much?\\n I know that!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 64,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(I don't want to make Nino or Miku\\n have these kinds of face, either!!\\n But...!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "It doesn't matter.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 66,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 67,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "That's right, it won't be for nothing.\\nI'll make you say you like me for sure, Fu-kun.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 68,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Even I will not give up\\nuntil I change your feelings, Futaro.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 69,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "I'm sorry, Uesugi-san, but\\nI'll be cheering for everyone too!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 70,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "I do not intend to approve\\nof your choice either.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 71,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 72,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Hey, Futaro-kun?\\nCould you have imagined it would turn out like this?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 73,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 74,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(It's not like I couldn't imagine it.\\n But still, this is the best way.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 75,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(My resolve, and their resolve.\\n Those two things will never overlap,\\n no matter what%p-2;――%p;)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 76,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(The conversation remained at a standstill\\n as the night went on.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}